title: Police Officers with Motorcycles During a Ceremony
description: A group of uniformed police officers stand together on a sunny street beside several motorcycles, including prominently featured front wheels. The motorcycles have "Electra Glide" written on them. The back of the photograph includes a stamp from the Miami Herald and a date of Jan 24 '72.
